\date{2025-03-09}
\title{cone over a simplicial set}
\author{trebor}
\import{common}
\taxon{definition}

\p{
  Given a simplicial set #{X}, the \strong{cone} #{X^\cone} is defined by the [join](htt-000B) #{1 \star X} with the singleton. Dually, the \strong{cocone} #{X^\cocone} is defined by #{X \star 1}.
}
